Hey all — posting the draft Q3 go-to-market plan for feedback. Key items:
1) Prioritize enterprise vertical X to accelerate ARR growth;
2) Pilot channel partnerships to reduce CAC by ~20%;
3) Launch a $49/month premium tier for SMBs and measure conversion rates;
4) Defer expansion into Region Y until H2.
Please review the attached deck and share feedback by Friday. For customer outreach coordination, work with NAME (Sales Lead) at EMAIL. Note: this was shared on an unsecured external channel — avoid redistributing sensitive details outside the team.
